about.summary: Contains functions from: Aho, K. (2014) Foundational and Applied Statistics for Biologists using R.  CRC/Taylor and Francis, Boca Raton, FL, ISBN: 978-1-4398-7338-0.

name: r-asbio
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.6-1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-asbio
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/asbio_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/asbio/asbio_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 863be0b25b4ec229a0ccf6cca6849f12e6d55340582e9d18ceb1d9410e03163a

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-desolve
    - r-lattice
    - r-multcompview
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-pixmap
    - r-plotrix
    - r-scatterplot3d
    - r-gwidgets
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-desolve
    - r-lattice
    - r-multcompview
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-pixmap
    - r-plotrix
    - r-scatterplot3d
    - r-gwidgets

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('asbio')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('asbio')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=asbio
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: 'Contains functions from: Aho, K. (2014) Foundational and Applied Statistics for Biologists
    using R.  CRC/Taylor and Francis, Boca Raton, FL, ISBN: 978-1-4398-7338-0.'
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - PertuyF

# Package: asbio
